Package org.hkijena.jipipe.ui

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    JIPipeWorkbench
    Interface shared by all workbench UIs
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JIPipeDummyWorkbench
    A dummy implementation of JIPipeWorkbench that will trigger no errors, but will not work for various functions.
    JIPipeJsonExtensionInfoUI
    UI that shows some introduction
    JIPipeJsonExtensionWindow
    Window that displays JIPipeJsonExtension UIs
    JIPipeJsonExtensionWorkbench
    UI around a JIPipeJsonExtension
    JIPipeJsonExtensionWorkbenchPanel
    UI panel that contains references to an JIPipeJsonExtension UI
    JIPipeProjectInfoUI
    UI that gives an overview of a pipeline (shows parameters, etc.)
    JIPipeProjectWindow
    Window that holds an JIPipeProjectWorkbench instance
    JIPipeProjectWorkbench
    UI around an JIPipeProject
    JIPipeProjectWorkbenchPanel
    Panel that holds a reference to JIPipeProjectWorkbench
    JIPipeWorkbenchPanel
    Panel that contains a reference to its parent workbench
